      <section eId="sec_381_945">
        <num>381.945</num>
        <content>
          <p>In any deed in which the minerals are severed from the surface, the present owners of the surface rights may enter into a written agreement directing how the surface shall be reclaimed, and how the property shall be left after the extraction of the minerals, and in compliance with federal and state rules and regulations.</p>
